{"tid":816584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一機救全亞洲【超強颱風逼港】地庫曾遭淹頂 杏花邨裝抽水機感應器防禦","createTime":"2018-09-13T00:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T00:19:29.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"43f551a790d580fde6088223c301a954fbf23de7","tid":816584,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T00:17:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180913/58674075\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180913%2F58674075&d=RgSJ%2F8uwmlGOYU11IwcF3QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c820e92f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180913%2F58674075&h=8dffe80e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180913/58674075</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180912/small/1536757354_d86d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180912%2Fsmall%2F1536757354_d86d.png&h=281b33ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天文台暫料超強颱風「山竹」最大機會在4日後的周日（16日），以高達時速220公里的中心風力，在尖沙嘴天文台總部西南方100公里左右掠過，勢成歷來襲港最強風暴，呼籲市民做好充足準備及防禦措施。去年在10號波「天鴿」吹襲時嚴重水浸、地庫停車場遭風暴潮淹頂的杏花邨，管理公司已在停車場加裝<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">水浸感應器和抽水機</span>防禦，又在近海位置堆起沙包，如臨大敵。<br />\n<br />\n一聽個名已經知道勁....一定可以成個山竹同維港 D 水抽乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2fbad7efbf27ae571a1dca8061778edb4ee0d64","tid":816584,"uid":33868,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T00:18:54.000Z","msg":"呢部機廁所爆屎渠就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81eb0beae0dc6f543c287a7ee90d531408667c1f","tid":816584,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T00:19:29.000Z","msg":"俾少少錢搵19過黎座鎮啦"}]}